data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch nestled at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac, offering privacy & serenity on 0.27 acres. As you enter, you'll be greeted by vaulted ceilings, an open floor plan, & newer vinyl plank flooring throughout the upper & lower levels. The kitchen boasts sleek new stainless steel appliances, making meal preparation a delight, while the main floor laundry adds practicality to your daily routine. Venture downstairs to discover a walkout basement with daylight windows, complete with a recreation room & pool table, perfect for entertaining. The potential for a 4th bedroom in the basement, already plumbed for a full bath, offers flexibility and space for guests or a second primary suite. Don't wait, schedule your showing today!
